# NyxButton

A button component with customizable themes, sizes, and styles.

## Usage

```vue
<NyxButton theme="primary" size="lg">Click me</NyxButton>
```

## Props

- `type`: The type of the button. Can be `button`, `submit`, or `reset`. Default is `button`.
- `theme`: The theme of the button. Can be `primary`, `secondary`, `success`, `danger`, `warning` or `info`. Default is `default`.
- `size`: The size of the button. Can be `xs`, `sm`, `md`, `lg`, or `xl`. Default is `md`.

